Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.30,0:24:30.28,TitleEP,en,0,0,240,,The Sea is Scary
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.30,0:24:30.28,TitleEP,en,0,0,90,,It's Onigoroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.30,0:24:30.28,NoteOnAnime,en,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}Look forwards for it!